speech:
Physical Symptoms:- 

    Changes in eating habits: Significant fluctuations in appetite, excessive food restriction, binge eating, or compulsive overeating.    
    Weight changes: Rapid weight loss, weight gain, or difficulty maintaining a healthy weight.
    Body image issues: Extreme preoccupation with body weight, shape, or appearance.
    Digestive problems: Constipation, diarrhea, bloating, or abdominal pain.
    Physical exhaustion: Fatigue, weakness, or dizziness.
    Hair loss: Thinning hair or hair loss.
    Skin problems: Dry, brittle skin or nails.
